	<main id="main">
	<section id="aboutUs" class="wow fadeInUp">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="section-header">
				<h2>About Us</h2>
				<p>Know us better</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-lg-12">
				<h2>About Us</h2>
				<p>
					<b>A GROUP OF YOUNG ACTORS AND DIRECTORS TO ENGAGE, INSPIRE AND
						CHALLENGE AUDIENCES WITH OUR WORK RANGING FROM THE CLASSICS TO THE
						CONTEMPORARY</b>
				</p>
				<p>The Being Association theatre group was formed in 2013 by a
					group of young fellow actors and directors to engage, inspire and
					challenge audiences with theatrical productions that range from the
					classics to contemporary works. From its inception, we have
					produced significant number of plays and performed at prominent art
					platforms of the country including the prestigious theatre
					festivals. We train and support the next generation of theatre
					artists by conducting theatre workshops periodically under the
					guidance of professionally trained and talented theatre
					practitioners. The occasional reading sessions by Being Association
					theatre group endeavours to stimulate the literary culture that
					empowers both artists and the audience. Apart from staging our
					plays, holding the reading sessions and conducting workshops, we
					also organise an annual theatre festival to recognise, promote and
					circulate new original Hindi plays. We continue to enrich the
					theatre movement in the future. We continue to celebrate the
					essential power of the theatre to illuminate the collective
					consciousness of humanity.</p>
			</div>
		</div>

	</section>





